item.title: CVE-2021-24540|2024-08-03T19:35:19.842Z -- unknown -- wonder%20video%20embed
item.description: The Wonder Video Embed WordPress plugin before 1.8 does not escape parameters of its wonderplugin_video shortcode, which could allow users with a role as low as Contributor to perform Stored XSS attacks.
